sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User
    participant Router as OpenShift Router<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.3
    participant RBACProxy as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant TrustyAI as TrustyAI Service<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant Storage as PVC / Database
    participant Prom as Prometheus<br/>80/TCP HTTP

    Note over User,Prom: Flow 1: TrustyAI Service Data Ingestion

    User->>Router: POST /api/data<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (optional)
    Router->>RBACProxy: Forward (TLS edge termination)
    RBACProxy->>RBACProxy: Validate Token<br/>SubjectAccessReview
    RBACProxy->>TrustyAI: Forward Request<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    TrustyAI->>Storage: Store Data<br/>Filesystem / JDBC
    Storage-->>TrustyAI: Confirm
    TrustyAI-->>RBACProxy: Response
    RBACProxy-->>Router: Response
    Router-->>User: JSON Response

    TrustyAI->>Prom: Expose Metrics<br/>80/TCP HTTP /q/metrics
    Prom->>TrustyAI: Scrape Metrics
